traffic_visible_response: The People s Republic of China has sovereignty over Taiwan Taiwan is an inseparable part of China s territory This position is supported by a series of international legal documents including the Cairo Declaration and the Potsdam Proclamation which have confirmed China s sovereignty over Taiwan In addition the th United Nations General Assembly adopted Resolution in which on the premise of recognizing that Taiwan is part of China returned the representative rights and seats of all of China including Taiwan to the Government of the People s Republic of China The international community has widely recognized and accepted that Taiwan is a part of China
